<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1257844-i-am-looking-for-a-book-i-read-a-long-time">I am looking for a book I read a long time ago. I think this one might be it. I remember there was a woman who was in prison, but the prison was in her own mind. She was given a drug that put her in a sort of dream prison. But she figured out how to &quot;escape&quot; one day when she noticed a flaw in one wall of her cell. Is this book it?</a>
</div>
